0.1.name: wordpress/the-social-links
0.1.description:
The Social Links plugin adds a widget to your WordPress website allowing you to display icons linking to your social profiles.

Supported networks:

  • Google+
  • Facebook
  • Twitter
  • Linkedin
  • YouTube
  • Delicous
  • LastFM
  • MySpace
  • Vimeo
  • StumbleUpon
  • orkut
  • Google Buzz
  • FriendFeed
  • Dribbble
  • YouVersion
  • And many more

Future features:

  • Custom template tag
  • Shortcode for insertion into WordPress posts

For support and feature requests head to digitalleap.co.za
